1.desc: There's nothing special about Noel's first implementation, but the enemies do grow stronger over time, so even novices may challenge it.
1.name: Hall of Challengers

10.desc: A trial program that tests how much damage  you can inflict in a short amount of time. Try to make your attacks more efficient!
10.name: General Attack Drill

11.desc: This trial program will test your limits  until you use the last of your strength.  Consider your options and go forth with a solid group!
11.name: Endless Corridor

12.desc: A trial program exclusive to male Units.  Strong opponents await to test  every last drop of your potential.
12.name: Courageous Assault

13.desc: A trial program exclusive to female Units.  Strong opponents await to test  every last drop of your potential.
13.name: Graceful Assault

14.desc: A trial program made for Grand Gaia adventurers.  Here you will face the gods anew as a test of your true power.
14.name: Recalling Order

15.desc: A trial program made for Ishgria adventurers.  Here you will face the demons anew as a test of your true power.
15.name: Recalling Bondage

16.desc: A trial program where you fight to the end using only Thunder and Light type Units. Test your limits under these demanding restrictions!
16.name: Flash of Lightning

17.desc: A trial program where you fight to the end using only Fire and Dark type Units. Test your limits under these demanding restrictions!
17.name: Flame of Darkness

18.desc: A trial program where you fight to the end using only Water and Earth type Units. Test your limits under these demanding restrictions!
18.name: Sea of Trees

19.desc: A training program to test how much Spark damage you can produce before defeating a foe. Requires expert knowledge of attack capabilities.
19.name: Relentless Practice

2.desc: A new trial program for challengers who seek basic battle practice.  Even new Summoners can use it to test their strength  and collect experience.
2.name: Proof of Power

20.desc: A system created to test your limits and endurance. Do the best you can against the never-ending hordes of foes coming your way!
20.name: Eternal Crusade

3.desc: A trial program exclusive to Earth Units.  How will you beat your foes under such conditions?  Here, your summoning skills will be tested.
3.name: Bound to Earth

4.desc: A trial program exclusive to Fire Units.  How will you beat your foes under such conditions?  Here, your summoning skills will be tested.
4.name: Bound to Fire

5.desc: A trial program exclusive to Dark Units.  How will you beat your foes under such conditions?  Here, your summoning skills will be tested.
5.name: Bound to Darkness

6.desc: A trial program exclusive to Water Units. How will you beat your foes under such conditions? Here, your summoning skills will be tested.
6.name: Bound to Water

7.desc: A trial program exclusive to Thunder Units. How will you beat your foes under such conditions? Here, your summoning skills will be tested.
7.name: Bound to Thunder

8.desc: A trial program exclusive to Light Units. How will you beat your foes under such conditions? Here, your summoning skills will be tested.
8.name: Bound to Light

9.desc: A trial program exclusive to 6-star rarity Units or below. Can you use your maxed out Units  to the full extent of their potential?
9.name: Six Stars' Assault
